\c 12
\s USamuweli ukhuluma ngokuthembeka kwakhe
\p
\v 1 USamuweli wasesithi kuIsrayeli wonke: Khangelani, ngililalele ilizwi lenu kukho konke elakutsho kimi\x + 8.5,19,20.\x*, sengibeke inkosi phezu kwenu\x + 10.24. 11.14,15.\x*.
\v 2 Khathesi-ke, khangelani, inkosi iyahamba phambi kwenu\x + 8.20. Nani 27.17.\x*; mina sengimdala, sengiyimpunga, khangelani, lamadodana ami akini; mina-ke ngihambile phambi kwenu kusukela ebutsheni bami kuze kube lamuhla\x + 8.1-5.\x*.
\v 3 Khangelani, ngi\add lapha\add*; fakazani limelane lami phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* laphambi kogcotshiweyo wayo\x + 10.1. 12.5. 24.6. 26.9,11,16. 2 Sam. 1.14,16.\x*: Ngithethe inkabi kabani? Loba ngithethe ubabhemi kabani\x + Nani 16.15. 1 Thes. 2.5.\x*? Ngiqilibezele bani\x + Dute. 28.33.\x*? Ngicindezele bani\x + Dute. 28.33.\x*? Ngemukele kubani isivalamlomo ukuze ngiphofuze amehlo ami ngawo? Njalo ngizakubuyisela kini\x + Dute. 16.19.\x*.
\v 4 Basebesithi: Kawusiqilibezelanga\x + Dute. 28.33.\x*, kawusicindezelanga\x + Dute. 28.33.\x*, njalo kawemukelanga lalutho esandleni samuntu.
\v 5 Wasesithi kibo: IN\nd kosi\nd* ingumfakazi imelene lani logcotshiweyo wayo ungumfakazi lamuhla\x + 10.1. 12.5. 24.6. 26.9,11,16. 2 Sam. 1.14,16.\x* ukuthi kalitholanga lutho esandleni sami. Bathi: Ingumfazaki\x + Eks. 21.16. 22.4.\x*.
\s Indlela uNkulunkulu amphatha ngayo uIsrayeli
\p
\v 6 USamuweli wasesithi ebantwini: KuyiN\nd kosi\nd* eyenza uMozisi loAroni, eyenyusa oyihlo elizweni leGibhithe\x + Mika 6.4.\x*.
\v 7 Khathesi-ke, manini njalo ngahlulelane lani phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngezenzo zonke ezilungileyo zeN\nd kosi\nd* eyazenza kini lakuboyihlo\x + Isa. 1.18. 5.3,4. Mika 6.2,3.\x*.
\v 8 Lapho uJakobe esefikile eGibhithe\x + Gen. 46.5,6.\x*, oyihlo bakhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 2.23.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* yasithuma oMozisi loAroni, abakhupha oyihlo eGibhithe, babenza bahlala kulindawo\x + 10.18. Eks. 3.10. 4.14-16.\x*.
\v 9 Sebeyikhohliwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo\x + Hlu. 3.7.\x*, yabathengisa esandleni sikaSisera induna yebutho leHazori\x + Hlu. 4.2. Dute. 32.30.\x*, lesandleni samaFilisti\x + Hlu. 3.31. 10.7. 13.1.\x*, lesandleni senkosi yakoMowabi\x + Hlu. 3.12.\x*; basebesilwa bemelene labo.
\v 10 Basebekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni bathi: Sonile, ngoba siyilahlile iN\nd kosi\x + Hlu. 10.10. Hlu. 3.9.\x*\nd*, sakhonza oBhali laboAshitarothi\x + Hlu. 2.13.\x*. Kodwa khathesi sophule esandleni sezitha zethu, sizakukhonza\x + Hlu. 10.15.\x*.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasithuma uJerubali\x + Hlu. 6.14,32.\x*, loBhedani\x + Hlu. 12.13-15. Hlu. 13.24,25.\x*, loJefitha\x + Hlu. 11.1.\x*, loSamuweli\x + 7.10-13.\x*, yalikhulula esandleni sezitha zenu inhlangothi zonke, laselihlala livikelekile.
\v 12 Lapho libona ukuthi uNahashi inkosi yabantwana bakoAmoni yeza ukumelana lani\x + 10.27. 11.1.\x*, lathi kimi: Hatshi, kodwa inkosi izasibusa\x + 8.5,19.\x*; kanti iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu yayiyinkosi yenu\x + 8.7. 10.19. Hlu. 8.23.\x*.
\v 13 Khathesi-ke, khangelani\x + 10.24.\x*, inkosi elayikhethayo, elayicelayo\x + 8.5. 9.20.\x*; khangelani-ke, iN\nd kosi\nd* imisile inkosi phezu kwenu\x + 9.16,17. Hos. 13.11.\x*.
\v 14 Uba liyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* liyikhonza lilalela ilizwi layo, lingawuvukeli umlomo weN\nd kosi\nd*, khona lina, lani kanye lenkosi ezabusa phezu kwenu lizalandela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 12.24. Dute. 6.2. Josh. 24.14.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa uba lingalilaleli ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa livukela umlomo weN\nd kosi\x + Levi 26.14. Josh. 24.20.\x*\nd*, isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sizamelana lani\x + 5.9.\x*, njengoba samelana laboyihlo\x + 12.9.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Lakhathesi manini, libone linto enkulu iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayenza phambi kwamehlo enu\x + Eks. 14.13.\x*.
\v 17 Angithi lamuhla kuyisivuno sengqoloyi\x + Zaga 26.1.\x*? Ngizakhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni njalo izanika umdumo lezulu\x + Jak. 5.16.\x*, ukuze lazi libone ukuthi ububi benu bukhulu elibenze emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* ngokuzicelela inkosi\x + 8.7.\x*.
\v 18 USamuweli wasekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, iN\nd kosi\nd* yasinika umdumo lezulu mhlalokho; ngakho bonke abantu bayesaba kakhulu iN\nd kosi\nd* loSamuweli\x + Eks. 14.31. Ezra 10.9.\x*.
\v 19 Bonke abantu basebesithi kuSamuweli: Khulekela izinceku zakho eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho, ukuze singafi; ngoba sengezelele ezonweni zethu zonke lobububi bokuzicelela inkosi\x + 12.23. Eks. 9.28. 10.17.\x*.
\p
\v 20 USamuweli wasesithi ebantwini: Lingesabi; lina lenze bonke lobububi, kodwa lingaphambuki ekuyilandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa likhonze iN\nd kosi\nd* ngenhliziyo yenu yonke.
\v 21 Njalo lingaphambuki ngoba \add linga\add*landela izinto eziyize\x + Dute. 11.16.\x* ezingasizi lutho ezingakhululiyo, ngoba ziyize\x + Jer. 16.19. Hab. 2.18. 1 Kor. 8.4.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiyikubatshiya abantu bayo\x + 1 Kho. 8.57. Hlab. 94.14.\x* ngenxa yebizo layo elikhulu\x + Josh. 7.9. Hlab. 106.8. Jer. 14.21. Hez. 20.9,14,22.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yathokoza ukulenza libe ngabantu bayo\x + Dute. 7.7,8.\x*.
\v 23 Mina-ke kakube khatshana lami ukuthi ngone eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngokuyekela ukulikhulekela\x + 12.19.\x*; kodwa ngizalifundisa\x + 1 Kho. 8.36. 2 Lan. 6.27. Hlab. 27.11. Zaga 4.11.\x* indlela enhle lelungileyo\x + Jer. 6.16.\x*.
\v 24 Kuphela yesabani iN\nd kosi\nd*, liyikhonze ngeqiniso ngenhliziyo yenu yonke\x + 12.14.\x*, ngoba bonani\x + Isa. 5.12.\x* okukhulu elenzele khona\x + Nani 16.26.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa uba liphikelela lisenza okubi, lina kanye lenkosi yenu\x + Dute. 28.36.\x* lizachithwa\x + Nani 16.26.\x*.